data.description: Country life yet centrally located for easy access to Goose Creek, Summerville, Moncks Corner, Cross & boat landing.   Enjoy sitting on your covered front porch sipping your coffee & listening to nature.   This 2008 very well, taken care of home sits on 2 acres & features an open floor plan, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, living room, family room, wood fireplace (can be converted to gas) kitchen with bar, dining area & laundry room. The owners suit features a separate tub /shower & double vanity.   Outside you have utilities already in place for another home (electric & sewer) 2 sheds & a carport to convey.   Put this on your list to see today!   Everything being sold as is.  Buyer to verify any and all information necessary including schools.   Roof installed in 2018
